annotationA: Enhancer of yellow 1 is a TAF9 protein and a main component of the Transcription factor II D (TFIID) complex. TFIID is involved in recruiting the transcription machinery to core promoters and organizing specific enhancer-promoter interactions
annotationB: H3 histone acetyltransferase activity; H4 histone acetyltransferase activity; histone acetyltransferase activity; chromatin binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: muscle organ development; chromatin remodeling; histone H3 acetylation; histone acetylation; axon target recognition; histone H4 acetylation; regulation of transcription, DNA-templated; dendrite morphogenesis
